{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_04_03",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 04 03",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――最終予選を勝利で飾ったトリエル",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――TRINITYAiLE emerged victorious in the final qualifying round.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.13333333333333333,
      "endTime": 2.513333315319486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その後、瑠依の部屋へ集まることになった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They later gathered in Rui's room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.513333315319486,
      "endTime": 5.173333295186364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 5.13333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "まあ、何はともあれ\nすみれちゃんが無事、こっちに来られて良かったわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ in any case‚\nI'm glad Sumire-chan made it here safely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.033333333333333,
      "endTime": 11.741836865743002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 11.933333333333302
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。大雨で新幹線が止まるなんて\n不安でしかたなかっただろうし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know‚ right? The Shinkansen stopping because of heavy rain…\nShe must have been so worried…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.933333333333334,
      "endTime": 18.06632636388143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "……二人は、全然、怒らないんだね\n大事なライブに間に合わなかったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You two aren't angry at all.\nEven though I missed such an important live performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.266666666666666,
      "endTime": 25.053922716776533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 18.266666666666698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "もう……何回同じことを言わせる気？\nすみれには何も責任ないんだから、自分を責めない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…How many times are you going to make me say the same thing?\nSumire is not responsible for anything‚ so don't blame yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.266666666666666,
      "endTime": 32.973786894480384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 25.266666666666698
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "逆に、これ以上引きずるなら、別の意味で怒るわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you keep dwelling on it‚ I'll get angry for a different reason.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.166666666666664,
      "endTime": 37.10650798479716,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 33.16666666666671
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 37.306507984797165
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "う……ごめんなさい。そうだよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh… I'm sorry. You're right…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.306507984797165,
      "endTime": 42.189841477076214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 42.38984147707622
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ\nせやけど今回、前乗りしていれば防げたんは事実",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ now\nBut it's true that if you had traveled there the day before‚ this could have been prevented.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.38984147707622,
      "endTime": 48.50625869433085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 48.6898414770762
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、そうしなかった\nすみれちゃん家の事情もあったんやろうけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you didn't do that.\nI'm sure there were circumstances at Sumire-chan's home.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6898414770762,
      "endTime": 53.78984166781106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 53.989841477076205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "よく考えたら、うちら、すみれちゃんの実家のこと\nあんま知らんかったなぁって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ we don't really know much about Sumire-chan's family‚ do we?\ndo we?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.989841477076205,
      "endTime": 60.76004535357156,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったよね。話す機会もなかったから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. There was never a chance to talk about it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.96004535357155,
      "endTime": 64.75106579462685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 60.960045353571594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "私の家って、むかーしから続いてる酒屋さんなの\n自分達でお酒も造ってる、造り酒屋ってやつ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My family runs a sake brewery that's been around for generations.\nWe make our own sake‚ it's called a \"kura.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.95106579462686,
      "endTime": 73.1677323023478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 64.95106579462689
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんとお母さん、それにお兄ちゃん\nあと、少ないけど従業員さんがいて、切り盛りしててね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My father‚ mother‚ and older brother‚\nand we have a few employees who help us run the business.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.36773230234778,
      "endTime": 80.31163269678747,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 73.36773230234783
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 80.50106563568113
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "へえ……代々続いてる家族経営……\nなんや、歴史を感じるなあ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… A family business that's been passed down for generations…\nIt feels like it's steeped in history.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.50106563568113,
      "endTime": 88.00106544494626,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 88.20106563568112
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "ただ最近、お父さんがぎっくり腰やっちゃって……\n動けなくなっちゃったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But recently‚ my dad threw out his back…\nHe can't move.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.20106563568112,
      "endTime": 94.00573673248287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 94.20573673248286
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "すぐに良くなるって話だったし\nお店も酒蔵も、ギリギリ作業は回ってたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They said he'd get better soon‚\nand the shop and brewery were just barely managing to operate.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.20573673248286,
      "endTime": 100.01179113388056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 100.21179113388061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "けど……天気が凄く悪くなるってニュースで聞いて\nしっかり浸水対策しないとって話になったの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… we heard on the news that the weather was going to be really bad‚\nso we had to take proper measures to prevent flooding…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.21179113388061,
      "endTime": 108.17229022979734,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "そう……それで、お父さんが動けない分\nすみれも手伝うことになったのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… So since your father couldn't move‚\nyou had to help out‚ Sumire.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.3784578005473,
      "endTime": 114.29410416285198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 108.37845780054757
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "うーんとね……私からやるって言ったの\nお母さん達は、気にしないで東京行きなさいって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… I volunteered to do it.\nMy mom and the others told me not to worry and just go to Tokyo‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.47845780054728,
      "endTime": 122.24165503184,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 114.47845780054767
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 122.44512446721366
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "だけど……どうしても放っておけなかったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but… I couldn't just leave them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.44512446721404,
      "endTime": 126.09281147321074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "私じゃ、大した手助けにはならないかもしれない\nそれでも……なにか、出来ることをしないとって思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I might not be much help‚\nbut… I felt like I had to do something‚ anything I could.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.29281147321075,
      "endTime": 133.831859000524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 126.29281147321103
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 134.031859000524
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_04_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんは家族思いのええ子やなあ\nご両親も鼻高々やろなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sumire-chan‚ you're such a good girl who cares about her family.\nYour parents must be very proud of you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.031859000524,
      "endTime": 140.2594326814017,
